# SmartGarden Environment Variables

Copy to `.env.local` for client, `.env` for firmware, and set in Supabase/Fly.io dashboards.

## Firmware (PlatformIO)
WIFI_SSID=your_wifi_ssid
WIFI_PASSWORD=your_wifi_password
MQTT_BROKER=localhost
MQTT_PORT=1883

## Supabase
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.com
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_anon_key
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your_service_role_key

## HiveMQ Cloud (Production)
MQTT_BROKER=your-broker.hivemq.cloud
MQTT_PORT=8883
MQTT_USERNAME=sg_bridge
MQTT_PASSWORD=your_mqtt_password

## Device Registration PSK
DEVICE_PSK=your-32-char-random-psk-here

## Fly.io (MQTT Bridge)
FLY_API_TOKEN=your_fly_api_token
